  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Hunting!</strong> is a turn-based strategy RPG focused on managing and developing new heroes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Train your heroes so they are ready for the final battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Hero Management</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227710/extras/4fd136446d77aaa8eb7b3b4aaf765831.avif?t=1750933861\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227710/extras_big/4fd136446d77aaa8eb7b3b4aaf765831.avif?t=1750933861 width=800 height=224 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hire incomplete heroes.<br>Train them and build a complete team.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Exploration and Combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227710/extras/cb25f0c99b3d36e4be0d13a0dccd9e41.avif?t=1750933861\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227710/extras_big/cb25f0c99b3d36e4be0d13a0dccd9e41.avif?t=1750933861 width=800 height=224 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore regions to achieve your objectives.<br>During exploration, engage in numerous battles alongside your heroes in a brief SRPG-based combat system.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Hunting!</strong> is a turn-based strategy RPG focused on managing and developing new heroes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Train your heroes so they are ready for the final battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Hero Management</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227710/extras/4fd136446d77aaa8eb7b3b4aaf765831.avif?t=1750933861\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227710/extras_big/4fd136446d77aaa8eb7b3b4aaf765831.avif?t=1750933861 width=800 height=224 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hire incomplete heroes.<br>Train them and build a complete team.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Exploration and Combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227710/extras/cb25f0c99b3d36e4be0d13a0dccd9e41.avif?t=1750933861\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227710/extras_big/cb25f0c99b3d36e4be0d13a0dccd9e41.avif?t=1750933861 width=800 height=224 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore regions to achieve your objectives.<br>During exploration, engage in numerous battles alongside your heroes in a brief SRPG-based combat system.</p>",
